Name: Meow-Jong
About the game: Meow-Jong is a modern take on the classic puzzle game Mahjong Solitaire, but with cats! Pounce into this Feline Frenzy! Meow-Jong is the purrrrrrrfect game for children and adults alike. It's a CAT-tastic way to spend your day! Packed with over 100 boards! Useful feline abilities! Stuck? Use your sharp eyes for move hints Don't see a move? Swipe your paw to reshuffle the board or backtrack to Undo your last moves Test your skills! Use your cat-like reflexes to 3-star every board!
